  "texts": [
    "We enlisted the expertise of professional designers to manually annotate the decoration styles and spatial functions of the ADSSFID-49 dataset.",
    "The decoration style annotations encompass seven categories: \"Contemporary style\", \"Chinese style\", \"Nordic style\", \"Japanese style\", \"European style\", \"Industrial style\", and \"American style\".",
    "The spatial function annotations also consist of seven categories: \"Children's room\", \"Study room\", \"Bedroom\", \"Bathroom\", \"Living room\", \"Dining room\", and \"Kitchen\".",
    "The distribution of the different categories of images is shown in Table 1.",
    "From Table 1, we can observe that in the ADSSFID-49 dataset, when sorted by a decoration style, the \"Contemporary style\" has the highest number of images (5153 images), while the \"Japanese style\" has the fewest (2108 images)."
  ],
